<h2>A private market</h2>
<p>Shinobiri is a place for people who want to sell and/or buy goods discreetly.</p>
<h5>-</h5>
<h5><i class="material-icons">warning</i> Rules:</h5>
<ol>
  <li>All stores are private without exception.</li>
  <li>Sellers decide who they invite to their shops.</li>
  <li>Purchases are only possible with Bitcoins or Ethers.<li>Users are required to have a PO BOX to create an account.</li>
  <li>Users are responsible for their transactions.</li>
  <li>Spam will not be tolerated.</li>
  <li>Problematic users will be banned without warning.</li>
  <li>Rules are subject to change without notice.</li>
  <li><small>work in progress</small>...</li>
</ol>
<h5>-</h5>
<h5>How it works:</h5>
<p>You do a search for the item you're looking for. Once you confirm the item you're looking for a notification is sent to the users with that item. It is up to the seller if they want to invite you to their trust or not.</p>
<h5>-</h5>
<h5>About the name:</h5>
<p>The name comes from Ninjutsu's <i>Shinobi-iri,</i> the art of stealth, the abilities of ninjas to remain unseen and undetected.</p>
